{"id": "ChIJfwjgK--5woARkB5GmA5KHe4", "rating": 4.9, "userRatingCount": 421, "displayName": {"text": "CHICHA San Chen - Koreatown", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJfwjgK--5woARkB5GmA5KHe4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25FMU0wMXJSMEpXWlZJd1FraG5SM0JsTlZsVmMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love this place! They focus on high quality of teas. I’m soo glad they open up in ktown. First time I tried it was in Vegas and I was obsessed with the tea! Now I know why it michelin star quality.\n\nThe ambiance is cute, very fresh, relaxing, as. Vibes, have some seatings and you get 40mins free parking validated next to the store.\n\nThe service is amazing, everyone’s friendly and explained really well what their tea is about and their most famous selections!\n\nI love the taro bubble and the plenty of refreshing options that focused on clean, high quality tea.\nI will definitely comeback to try their other options.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love this place! They focus on high quality of teas. I’m soo glad they open up in ktown. First time I tried it was in Vegas and I was obsessed with the tea! Now I know why it michelin star quality.\n\nThe ambiance is cute, very fresh, relaxing, as. Vibes, have some seatings and you get 40mins free parking validated next to the store.\n\nThe service is amazing, everyone’s friendly and explained really well what their tea is about and their most famous selections!\n\nI love the taro bubble and the plenty of refreshing options that focused on clean, high quality tea.\nI will definitely comeback to try their other options.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Katrin Mendoza", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111240994049911798244/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFOCibb__pWle_hT_wGCrZ6NVygKSuuLXjSvcwBTFO2gafAgOF=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-29T20:00:27.357651792Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25FMU0wMXJSMEpXWlZJd1FraG5SM0JsTlZsVmMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25FMU0wMXJSMEpXWlZJd1FraG5SM0JsTlZsVmMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9ef2be0087f:0xee1d4a0e98461e90"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfwjgK--5woARkB5GmA5KHe4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214clRWODFVM3BDVTJwcVZuUlZXWFJ2UzBscFNWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Just tried the newly opened Chi Cha San Chen in Ktown and it did not disappoint. The tea quality is noticeably high—very clean and fragrant, not overly sweet, and you can really taste the difference compared to typical boba spots.\n\nI ordered the bubble milk tea and the mango drink, and both were super refreshing. The milk tea was smooth and well-balanced, and the fruit drink tasted fresh, not artificial at all. Also loved that the sweetness level feels more natural rather than syrup-heavy.\n\nThe store itself is clean and modern, and you can see the tea being brewed fresh, which is a nice touch. Staff were friendly and efficient even though it was busy.\n\nDefinitely a great addition to Ktown! I will be coming back to try more of their menu.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Just tried the newly opened Chi Cha San Chen in Ktown and it did not disappoint. The tea quality is noticeably high—very clean and fragrant, not overly sweet, and you can really taste the difference compared to typical boba spots.\n\nI ordered the bubble milk tea and the mango drink, and both were super refreshing. The milk tea was smooth and well-balanced, and the fruit drink tasted fresh, not artificial at all. Also loved that the sweetness level feels more natural rather than syrup-heavy.\n\nThe store itself is clean and modern, and you can see the tea being brewed fresh, which is a nice touch. Staff were friendly and efficient even though it was busy.\n\nDefinitely a great addition to Ktown! I will be coming back to try more of their menu.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ziqi Liu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112358455808079325663/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFsz7-yO5nhVCDl9fery5YcodBr3yUzV_fTI_g8w07q9azig=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-10T02:02:30.697237755Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214clRWODFVM3BDVTJwcVZuUlZXWFJ2UzBscFNWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214clRWODFVM3BDVTJwcVZuUlZXWFJ2UzBscFNWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9ef2be0087f:0xee1d4a0e98461e90"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfwjgK--5woARkB5GmA5KHe4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25RM09Xc3hjM0JSZDJoWGQwVlBUM1pSUlZGaFFWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Chicha San Chen in Koreatown is easily one of the best tea spots I’ve tried. The boba milk tea is absolutely perfect—rich, smooth, and perfectly balanced in sweetness. The boba itself stands out the most: incredibly chewy and packed with flavor, just the way it should be.\n\nI also tried the taro ball, and it was delicious—soft, slightly sweet, and a great addition to the drink. Their fruit teas are just as impressive, super refreshing and perfect if you’re looking for something lighter.\n\nOverall, everything tastes high-quality and thoughtfully made. Definitely a 5-star experience and a spot I’ll keep coming back to!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Chicha San Chen in Koreatown is easily one of the best tea spots I’ve tried. The boba milk tea is absolutely perfect—rich, smooth, and perfectly balanced in sweetness. The boba itself stands out the most: incredibly chewy and packed with flavor, just the way it should be.\n\nI also tried the taro ball, and it was delicious—soft, slightly sweet, and a great addition to the drink. Their fruit teas are just as impressive, super refreshing and perfect if you’re looking for something lighter.\n\nOverall, everything tastes high-quality and thoughtfully made. Definitely a 5-star experience and a spot I’ll keep coming back to!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bear", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107658432760563517938/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLHu62XD7Rqsa0hPtsP1rx3LGB58qeohyx4DrQG8mho76gog=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T03:51:22.053679014Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25RM09Xc3hjM0JSZDJoWGQwVlBUM1pSUlZGaFFWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25RM09Xc3hjM0JSZDJoWGQwVlBUM1pSUlZGaFFWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9ef2be0087f:0xee1d4a0e98461e90"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfwjgK--5woARkB5GmA5KHe4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxVGVEbFVhbmh3VVZGbVRtZDNSMnAzV1cxblpsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Taste so good！ I like 0 surge, the taste still great! Very good tea selection.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Taste so good！ I like 0 surge, the taste still great! Very good tea selection.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Riva Zhu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116899648587303084766/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOzIp9aTrcoFYlJ9KdV2PaUo8HGZN17KndUFEM2taY1tGxRCFh=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-01T19:46:30.176420786Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxVGVEbFVhbmh3VVZGbVRtZDNSMnAzV1cxblpsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/